{"tid":2496610,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"夢見kelly","createTime":"2021-04-20T02:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T02:57:03.000Z","uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"353025de12d77c76eacd9cf4a397b17bbf1a3f6a","tid":2496610,"uid":307910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T02:57:03.000Z","msg":"中學嘅環境，身邊嘅同學卻係我成個人生識嘅人，我印象中我好想約一個女仔出街，係放學嘅時候，正正見到kelly，企咗係我面前，唔知點解我同佢一句說話都無講，互相對目而笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我就開口先，其實琴日我都有一齊入去食紅豆沙<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，我係ig見到你食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁啱嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，係呀，真係咁啱得咁橋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後我哋就一齊笑鳩碗紅豆沙難食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當時嘅佢真係好靚，成個人好似粉藍色咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之後醒返，先知原來我同佢冇和好過，開返佢ig，先知佢早已經唔係我一直以來鍾意嘅粉藍色女仔<br />\n<br />\n已經變成一個久經歷練嘅女士<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cryalot.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n想問下邊度可以搵到一個好似10年前嘅kelly咁嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}